info.name: API Testing Collection
info.description:
This collection tests the Intergalactic Bank API for managing devices and predicting their prices.

ü™ê Quick Start  
Test Cases:  
Predict Prices: Run predictions for 10 devices using their specifications.  
Device Management:  
Add Devices: POST to add new devices.  
Retrieve Devices: GET to fetch all devices or specific device details by ID.  
üîç How to Use  
Run Collection: Select Run Collection from the menu to execute all tests in sequence.  
Check Results: Review the test results in the Test Results tab for success or failure messages.  
üîí Authorization  
Ensure you set up your API key at the collection level for all requests.

ü§ù Feedback  
If you have suggestions for additional test cases or improvements, please leave comments directly in the collection.

Retrieve a list of all devices

item.description:
This folder tests a commonly used workflow of creating new accounts and transferring funds between the two.

Because we expect all requests to succeed in this workflow, we have a **status check test** in the **folder-level Scripts tab**.
